    "Clever uses of public APIs to extract more details than they were meant to." : {
      "comment" : "Sensitivity tier description shown in onboarding and as the footer beneath the signal list on every advanced-tier category screen.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
