    "use the %@ calendar instead of %@" : {
      "comment" : "Region-mismatch sub-clause about calendar systems on the fingerprint summary sheet. First %@ is the user's chosen calendar name; second %@ is the baseline calendar for their region. Will be joined with other clauses by Oxford comma.",
