    "write dates as \"%@\" instead of \"%@\"" : {
      "comment" : "Region-mismatch sub-clause about date formatting on the fingerprint summary sheet. First %@ is the user's locale-formatted sample date; second %@ is the regional baseline. Will be joined with other clauses by Oxford comma.",
